{"questionId":"722de804","correctAnswer":"94","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Expand to standard form","content":"$(x-47)^2=1 \\Rightarrow x^2-94x+2209=1 \\Rightarrow x^2-94x+2208=0$<br/>So $a=1$, $b=-94$."},{"title":"Apply Vieta&apos;s sum formula","content":"$$\\text{sum of solutions}=\\frac{-b}{a}=\\frac{-(-94)}{1}=94$$<br/>The answer is <strong>94</strong>.","desmosExpressions":["y=(x-47)^2","y=1"]}]}